short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make all Devpost project winning projects

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Chrome extension allows you to add people with their Devpost username and give them the illusion of having all winning projects. The extension doesn't actually change state of the project, just gives the illusion that one did win every project. Just add the extension, type in the Devpost username and turn on spoofing!
